name: Fountainhead
overview:
Fountainhead,relocating services dubai,property management consultant,logistics support,corporate services uae,home searches services,Concierge services Dubai..

Fountainhead Services is based in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. It is not a “business” in the traditional sense ……… Put simply, Fountainhead was started as a pet project – a hobby, if you like – by the Managing Partner.

Having been an expat herself since the late 1990s and a veteran of relocations, the Managing Partner recognised first-hand the challenges faced by professionals – and their families – when they move to new countries……. and new cultures.

In todays’ age, the “heavy lifting” involved in relocations – e.g. the packing, the shipping, the delivery, etc. - is not an issue in most cases, as it is taken care of by the employer.

Fountainhead Managing Partner is a Londoner expat, a lawyer and holds an MSc from the London School of Economics. Shed has previously worked at KPMG and Lloyds Bank Group.

For More : http://fountainheadworldwide.com
